{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"cfd5b009b6","title":"给干观澜的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0c17a96291","index":0,"year":1948,"month":3,"day":31,"articleId":"cfd5b009b6"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji24","name":"毛泽东全集第24卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji24.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji24":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c49879e3ff","type":"paragraph","text":"给干观澜的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"cfd5b009b6"},{"id":"962327708a","type":"paragraph","text":"（1948年3月31日）观洞同志：来示磊。大有起色，极为欣感。去苏联治病是可以的，待秋李你到五台区，如果平绥线已打通，路上好走，即可和那边交涉前往，你即可去。此复顺祝健康！","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"cfd5b009b6"},{"id":"195fc214fc","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"cfd5b009b6"},{"id":"0fc4c6da66","type":"paragraph","text":"三月三十一日[1]王观端（1906-1982），浙江临海人。第二次内革命线争时期曾任《红色中华》总编辑，中华苏维埃共和国中央政府土地部副部长。红军长征到达院北后，历任中央农民委员会主任、陕甘宁边区统战委员会主任等职。1948年到苏联治病","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"cfd5b009b6"}],"page":{"id":"eb3168b099","publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"cfd5b009b6","start":186,"end":186}}}},"__N_SSG":true}